# Requirements
  * Local PMS Server
  * PHP cli 
  * PHP SQlite (PDO)
  * API key from TMDB (themoviedb.org)

# HowTo

  1) Scrape for EVERY cast member missing an image ( ONLY run this once a day )
      php scrape_tmdb.php --all

  2) Scrape for EVERY cast member updated within the last day missing an image ( run this HOURLY )
     php scrape_tmdb.php


